  <refsect1 id='description'><title>Description</title>
  <para>
    <command>rdnexusd</command><manvolnum>8</manvolnum> manages the interface
    between the Rivendell Radio Automation System and MusicMaster Nexus.
    It is normally configured by <command>rdadmin</command>
    <manvolnum>1</manvolnum> and invoked by <command>rdservice</command>
    <manvolnum>8</manvolnum>.
    There should only be one instance of
    <command>rdnexusd</command><manvolnum>8</manvolnum> running at any
    given time.
  </para>
  </refsect1>
  
